## Meeting Spaces

From worship gatherings to team planning sessions, our meeting spaces accommodate your group's needs.

**Chapel** - Beautiful worship and gathering space with seating for large groups up to 200 with full installed A/V system.

**Gym-**

- **Lakeside Room**- Smaller meeting space perfect for groups up to 40- A/V system available
- **Classrooms-** 4 classrooms available for breakout sessions, seminars, or meetings located in our gym.
- **Main Gym-** Large gathering room for up to 250 with full installed A/V system

