## Good to Know

- Full-service kitchen and customizable meal plans (dining for up to 120)
- Peaceful lakeside location, 30 miles NW of Fort Wayne, IN
- We do not host rentals for family gatherings, parties, or weddings
- **Rentals not available May through July**

